  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to provide an opportunity for patients with malignancies or bone
      marrow failure states who lack a suitable sibling donor to undergo allogeneic hematopoietic
      progenitor cell transplantation using cells from unrelated individuals or cord blood
      registries.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
