  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  &gt; 18 years of Age

          -  &lt; 70 years

          -  ECOG performance status 0, 1 or 2

          -  Left Ventricular Ejection Fraction &gt; 30%

          -  Creatinine clearance &gt; 40ml/min

          -  Transaminases &lt; 2X normal

          -  Total bilirubin &lt; 2X normal

          -  HIV seronegativity

          -  Weight &lt; 70kg for cord blood transplantation

          -  Ability to cover the cost of the transplant, necessary medications, and
             transportation/housing.

          -  Caregiver must be available while outpatient

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Greater than one antigen mismatch at HLA-A, B, C or DR plus one allele mismatch at
             HLA-A, B, C or DR
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
